{"tid":1693632,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【XYZ】向佐發聲：找回那個令我們驕傲的香港！","createTime":"2019-11-04T17:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T18:07:20.000Z","uid":231132,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7803443d1de0ddfeb3c64304c58420373a729753","tid":1693632,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:13:28.000Z","msg":"生在香港長在香港，我熱愛這片土地。很長時間了，香港處於動亂的狀態。我的心情，從一開始的不解，到憤怒，到如今的無奈。我希望做一些事情，找回那個令我們驕傲的香港。<br />\n<br />\n這個視頻講述的是我親身經歷的故事，雖然相隔很久，但每一個細節都刻在腦海裏，時不時告訴我這個世界的一些殘酷真相&mdash;種族歧視；時不時提醒我，無論何時何地自己都是一個中國人。我也希望，更多的年輕人耐心看完這個視頻，並理解我的歸屬感，從而找到屬於自己的歸屬感。<br />\n<br />\n願憑著我們每一個香港人的努力，還原這顆東方之珠的光芒。一名中國香港市民<br />\n<br />\n微博LINK: <a href=\"https://video.h5.weibo.cn/1034:4434999051493885/4434999488813101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.h5.weibo.cn%2F1034%3A4434999051493885%2F4434999488813101&d=giu1nYcgFqEI960N5jmVcad04xtnDtF9LgqILkRy7NQ%3D&h=bf6dc741\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.h5.weibo.cn/1034:4434999051493885/4434999488813101</a><br />\n<br />\nWho is 向佐?🤔"},{"pid":"8ed1c4f23eeb521472e542cb25d687d940e0b317","tid":1693632,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:16:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8545755c294e41efc3441031c7ea4e85114f3ad3","tid":1693632,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"向右？"},{"pid":"8e49e776bf74b83b67ac3167bfa5bff77edf803a","tid":1693632,"uid":318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:20:31.000Z","msg":"將身體溶入呢個節奏"},{"pid":"1cb01bcf81f57e03109a12b67380c3eda77bf85c","tid":1693632,"uid":263183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8545755c294e41efc3441031c7ea4e85114f3ad3","tid":1693632,"uid":167428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"向右？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T17:20:37.000Z","msg":"將身體融入呢個節奏?"},{"pid":"413fa1ebb6b67ae354f5ed03da5fa260ca9595b8","tid":1693632,"ui